race.description: Back To The Gift Hotel Handicap
race.comment: BRUZANI (13) just missed first up and then got too far back here last time well in the market. Draws inside today and Hill replaces the 2kg apprentice. Fitter again and is well-placed to win. CHARITIES (10) placed from the back at Donald first-up and then was heavily bet at Horsham and things didn't work out on the slow track. She has plenty up the sleeve and the step up to the mile suits. MANCHEGO (2) peaks and is knocking on the door. Maps well enough and has claims. KENTAHTEN (7) was going well before the flop at Kerang. Has a handy 3kg claim and won't be far away with some luck in the run. ELVIS (5) gets in well with the 4kg claim and was only beaten 2L at Colac. The extra 400m will suit him.
